                "game-id": "b6399e07408cff972b3e106b3a1f049b",
                "text": "Lawful effects often manipulate energy from law-aligned Outer Planes and are antithetical to chaotic divine servants or divine servants of chaotic deities. A creature with this trait is lawful in alignment.",
